140
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,970
Conservative treatment?

141
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,160
Wearing a plaster cast for three or four weeks.

142
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,710
By that time,

143
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,280
my right leg's muscles

144
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,610
