147
00:08:38,210 --> 00:08:39,559
Muscular atrophy?

148
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:43,500
Will it have any impact on you in the future?

149
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,990
Don't you think you are too nervous?

150
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:48,160
It won't.

151
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:51,510
