262
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,550
Can I participate in the competition

263
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:33,900
in five months?

264
00:13:34,470 --> 00:13:35,280
Competition?

265
00:13:35,950 --> 00:13:37,590
Are you kidding me?

266
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,640
Even the function may not be fully restored, okay?

267
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:45,280
Two weeks after the operation, your thigh,

268
00:13:45,310 --> 00:13:47,160
calf, and foot will be immobilized with a plaster cast.

269
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,400
After removing the sutures,

270
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,280
